CHANGE LOG
==========

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

0.2.1 - 2015-6-26
Added
- Post-Install scripting capabilities.

0.2.0 - 2015-6-23
Changes
- Ported to Python 3.
- PEP8 Compliance
Added
- Group package selection.

0.1.3 - 2015-6-14
Added
- AutoPartitioning as default disk creation scheme.

0.1.2 - 2015-06-10
Changes
- Kernel.org mirror instead of CentOS default location
Fixes
- User's password BUG resolved
- Whitespacing BUG resolved
- EPEL temporarily removed

0.1.1 - 2015-06-10
Added
- DHCP and STATIC IPv6 configuration options.
- Enhanced package selection to support WS class environments.

